Guardian of the Dark

Edit on GitHub

PreviousAmouri's MemoriesNextChocobo's Memories

Overview

UnlockClear Amouri's Memories (Chapter 5).
LocationAirship Hangar near Freja's Forge (Chapter 5).
Title -
Description Normal dungeon with no restrictions.
Floors 50F Bosses 10F, 20F, 30F, 40F, 50F
Change Crystals 0F, 49F Checkpoints 11F, 21F, 31F, 41F
Max Level - Bring Buddy Yes
Bring In Items Yes Take Out Items Yes
Shops/Duels Yes Den of Monsters Yes
Reapers Yes Bookmark Yes
Unidentified Equipment, Consumables
Rewards 1. Dark Apple (49F).
Chocobo's Max SP 6 7.
2. Dungeon added to Mirror of Memory.
3. Can unlock Chocobo's Memories.
4. Can unlock Pain for Gain.
